list.abstract: rank是T_sql 函数，rank()函数返回结果集分区内指定字段的值的排名，指定字段的值的排名是相关行之前的排名加一。

yingyinNormal.zh: 反对，不可任意猜测。反对有效。

yingyinNormal.en: Why don't you just go ahead and rank that number one?
Sir William Lucas, for instance, is a very agreeable man. And a good deal less self-important than some people half his rank.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比如威廉·卢卡斯爵士就是位很和蔼的人。跟他同一爵位的某些人比起来，他是那么温雅的好人。

yingyinNormal.en: I've often observed to Lady Catherine that her daughter seemed born to be a duchess, for she has all the superior graces of elevated rank.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我常说凯瑟琳夫人，她的女儿好像出生就是女公爵，因为她拥有贵族们所有的优雅。

yingyinNormal.en: Gentlemen, if I may interject, I've decided my rank will be captain. If it's good enough for Kirk, Crunch and Kangaroo, it's good enough for me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先生们，容我插一句，我决定我的军阶为上尉了，如果科克船长，嘎嘣脆船长和袋鼠船长都能胜任此职，那对我而言也不错。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, Question one: Rank the following aspects of Sheldon Cooper in order of appeal: Intelligence; ruthless attention to hygiene; playfulness; JAVA applet writing?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，问题1: 按吸引力程度给谢尔顿·库珀以下各方面排序，聪明，洁癖，有趣，Java程序编写？

yingyinNormal.en: I have fought against my better judgement, my family's expectation, the inferiority of your birth, my rank, all these things, and I'm willing to put them aside and ask you to end my agony.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在与世俗的看法，与我家族的期望对抗，与你的身世，与我的阶级对抗，我要把他们统统抛开，让你终结我的痛苦。

word_usage.usage:
rank表示“给……评级/评名次”时，既可作及物动词，也可作不及物动词。作及物动词时，rank后接名词或代词作宾语，也可接以名词充当补足语的复合宾语。例：
They ranked the tennis player the third in the world.
他们把这位网球运动员评为世界第三号选手。
